title: Life expectancy at birth in Germany 2017
yAxis: Life expectancy at birth in years
summary: In general Life expectancy at birth in years has stayed the same over the Year.
Life expectancy at birth in years is slightly increasing from 2010 to 2011, and lastly roughly constant from 2011 to 2012.
The most drastic increase took place within the Year 2010 and 2011.
The highest Life expectancy at birth in years, of value 80.54 was reached at Year 2012
The lowest Life expectancy at birth in years, of value 79.99 was reported at Year 2010
